There is no one too far gone

00:03:08.380 --> 00:03:19.480
Can't your eyes see, what can be done
With a little love

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:31.980
Just blow the dust from off the surface of
a tired and weary life,

00:03:31.980 --> 00:03:38.880
